                        "name": "willie",
                        "displayName": "Willie Alberty",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "As with any other PDF drawing operations, text is drawn using the current fill color of the content stream's (page's) graphic state:\n\n{code}\n$page->setFillColor(new Zend_Pdf_Color_Rgb(1, 0, 0));  \/\/ red\n{code}\n\n{{Zend_Pdf_Style}} objects allow you to set multiple attributes of the graphics state at once, but are not required.\n",
